{"tid":1553922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政黨可以有領袖，活動可以有搞手，但旗隊領袖是一個什麼概念？","createTime":"2019-09-08T18:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:20:18.000Z","uid":107060,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe796bcae7775a7a0f8adb4aa1071ad80dc0b7f","tid":1553922,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"政黨可以有領袖，活動可以有搞手，但旗隊領袖是一個什麼概念？<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n首先我翻查到的資料陳雲最遲7月8日已經在臉書主張舉美國，最遲7月14日沙田遊行已經有人高舉美國旗（註）。然後8月16日這個人(花旗參)在連登問「816遮打有無人會帶美國旗？」，8月17日這個人又在連登叫「美國旗手集合」，然後到今日9月8日他就自稱自己是「旗隊leader」，控訴別人騎劫，在帖文得到上千讚好。<br />\n<br />\n我再進一步翻查此人過去的帖文，有以下的發現。7月12日，此人(花旗參)在呼籲參選區議會及立法會，內文提到：「到e家仲係度講緊示威遊行先係主線其實真係錯晒......如果我地唔舖排定區議會搵人參選最終都係輸硬」。4月29日，此人(花旗參)發文「其實我唔明泛民抵𨳒同反逃犯條例有咩衝突」內文提到：「我唔理泛民係咪成日關鍵時刻做唔撚到野or係鬼，但呢刻你話因為佢而唔去遊行or反佢，咁姐係想通過?」<br />\n<br />\n我就不評論這兩則帖文，但相信各位大概可以理解這個人的背景吧。<br />\n<br />\n註：更新最遲7月13日上水遊行已經有人高舉美國旗。"},{"pid":"9762dda95cd4a5bc348977425bf94ff603c3285c","tid":1553922,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:37:04.000Z","msg":"[急!!!]9/9有班中學生等緊你地救！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5ad9e46879b05fc22ab42259eb191cd5f4a9ff32","tid":1553922,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:39:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c56616779fb542821597bb02cf92ab1d9c198286","tid":1553922,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d5f1eee982ba5951935da2bc3c9b97de1eeb93e","tid":1553922,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b706e16aaaaf53d815d37b5869f71b46613e5af","tid":1553922,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5f28295e58e3339553199497678973e3cabef2","tid":1553922,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f29da3948abbd8ec96c103231ba2930d7c8ffd","tid":1553922,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67586240c05d20db8b153a3d80483a1fbaa07a7d","tid":1553922,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}